data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Byron! This spacious and beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers over 2000 sq ft of luxurious living space, situated on an expansive 1/3-acre lot. Built in 2005 but with nearly new roof & HVAC,  this home boasts modern amenities and timeless charm, making it the perfect place for you. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere that radiates warmth and comfort. The well-designed floor plan features a formal dining room, and a stylish and functional kitchen, complete with a convenient breakfast bar and an eat-in area. LVP flooring throughout the main living areas adds a touch of sophistication while being easy to maintain. The spacious living room is the perfect place to unwind after a long day, with ample room for cozy furniture and entertainment. One of the standout features of this property is the covered patio, offering an outdoor oasis where you can relax and enjoy the serene surroundings, in the privacy of your fenced backyard. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional house your new home. Contact me today to schedule a private showing and experience the epitome of gracious living in Byron!
